Schott Zwiesel Congresso Champagne Glass (Set of 12)_
                    Toast the New Year in style                

                        With a Congresso stem in hand, I relax. And it's not the wine: It's the glass itself. This stem is as dignified as it is sturdy, offering a comforting weight. If it should tumble, the titanium-infused crystal won't easily shatter like some featherweight glasses. Schott Zwiesel delivers such impressive value with these glasses, it feels too good to be true.
